que a outra. Ap\u00f3s brincar algumas vezes com um amigo de mesmo peso, ele percebeu que quando est\u00e1 em uma extremidade, a gangorra se desequilibra para o lado dele (ou seja, ele fica na parte de baixo, e o amigo na parte de cima), mas quando eles trocam de lado, a gangorra se desequilibra para o lado do amigo.</p>\n<p>Sem entender a situa\u00e7\u00e3o, Jo\u00e3ozinho pediu ajuda a outro amigo de outra s\u00e9rie, que explicou que o comprimento do lado interfere no equil\u00edbrio da gangorra, pois a gangorra estar\u00e1 equilibrada quando</p>\n<div class=\"language-hs highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kt\">P_1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">C_1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">igual</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">P_2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">C_2</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>onde P_1 e P_2 s\u00e3o os pesos da crian\u00e7a no lado esquerdo e direito, respectivamente, e C_1 e C_2 s\u00e3o os comprimentos da gangorra do lado esquerdo e direito, respectivamente.</p>\n<p>Escreva uma fun\u00e7\u00e3o gangorra que recebe quatro inteiros P_1, C_1, P_2 e C_2, que s\u00e3o respectivamente, o peso da crian\u00e7a e o comprimento da gangorra do lado esquerdo e o o peso da crian\u00e7a e o comprimento da gangorra do lado direito.Se a gangorra estiver equilibrada, a fun\u00e7\u00e3o gangorra devolve 0. Se ela estiver desequilibrada de modo que a crian\u00e7a esquerda esteja na parte de baixo, a fun\u00e7\u00e3o gangorra devolve -1, sen\u00e3o, devolve 1.</p>\n<p>Por exemplo,</p>\n<div class=\"language-hs highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nf\">gangorra</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">30</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">100</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">60</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">50</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">==</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n<span class=\"nf\">gangorra</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">40</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">40</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">38</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">60</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">==</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"nf\">gangorra</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">35</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">80</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">35</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">75</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">==</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"nf\">gangorra</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">45</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">23</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">96</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">12</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">==</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"nf\">gangorra</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">74</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">12</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">65</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">48</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">==</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"nf\">gangorra</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">78</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">45</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">12</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">23</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">==</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Testes</h2>\n<div class=\"language-text highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;\n30\n100\n60\n50\n========\n0\n&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;\n\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;\n40\n40\n38\n60\n========\n1\n&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;\n\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;\n35\n80\n35\n75\n========\n-1\n&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;\n\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;\n45\n23\n96\n12\n========\n1\n&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;\n\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;\n74\n12\n65\n48\n========\n1\n&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;\n\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;\n78\n45\n12\n23\n========\n-1\n&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;\n</code></pre></div>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
